Company Overview of East Coast Asset Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
East Coast Asset Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm also provides financial planning and wealth management services such as, retirement planning, asset allocation planning, estate planning, risk management, and tax planning services. It primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. The firm also caters to individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, families, foundations, and endowments. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm invests in public equity and fixed income markets. It also invests in exchange traded funds and mutual funds. The firm employs f...
East Coast Asset Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm also provides financial planning and wealth management services such as, retirement planning, asset allocation planning, estate planning, risk management, and tax planning services. It primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. The firm also caters to individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, families, foundations, and endowments. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm invests in public equity and fixed income markets. It also invests in exchange traded funds and mutual funds. The firm employs fundamental and quantitative analysis to make its investments. It conducts in-house research to make its investments. East Coast Asset Management, LLC was founded in 2008 and is based in Essex, Massachusetts with additional offices in Boston, Massachusetts and Burlington, Massachusetts.
