About

 


home
contact
privacy policy

East Coast Asset Managementâ
            management team has been active in the Financial Services
            market for thirty-five years. We have focused on receivables
            management and servicing for the last six years.
Our current company was established in 2012 to work with
          small businesses that service Medical and Personal Care
          markets. East Coast partners with our business partners in managing 
          receivables that are both performing and nonperforming on consumer
          and commercial accounts. We work with each of our clients to enhance
          profitability and cash-flow.
We strive to rehabilitate non-performing debtors in an effort
          to allow the original service provider to reactivate their
          relationship with their client. Through structuring strategic
          periods for receivables acquisition we can improve our clients
          profitability and enhance our acquired portfolio values. Our
          compliance focus and respect for our debtors enables us to
          improve performance. 
Our goal is to establish long term relationships with
          established service providers. Working together on mutual
          objectives has proven to be profitable for all parties
          involved. 




 




