 EAST COAST ASSET Overview



												   East Coast Asset Management Llc. is an investment advisor that manages 417 MM dollars in regulatory AUM and has 14 employees, of which 10 perform investment advisory functions. The manager's has disclosed holdings from 12/31/12 to 03/31/17. The fund's latest filing disclosed 363MM in positions, representing 87% of the manager's regulatory AUM.
												



